title: Crazy Taxi Trilogy - Original Soundtrack (OST) [FLAC]
description:
This is the complete soundtrack from original Crazy Taxi Trilogy: Crazy Taxi (Dreamcast/PS2/Xbox), Crazy Taxi 2 (Dreamcast) & Crazy Taxi 3: High Roller (Xbox). 

All tracks 44kHZ 16-bbit FLAC files, remastered from lossless sources specifically for this compilation. All tracks uncensored.

02. Bad Religion - Hear It

09. The Offspring - Come Out Swinging 
10. The Offspring - One Fine Day 
11. The Offspring - No Brakes 
12. The Offspring - Walla Walla 
13. Methods Of Mayhem - Crash 
14. The Offspring - Special Delivery

16. Silverbullit - Raw Power Angel 
17. Brian Setzer - Ignition 
18. The Offspring - Want You Bad 
19. Bad Religion - Empty Causes 
20. Silverbullit - Boom Boom Boogie

Tracks 1 - 6 & 23 from Crazy Taxi 1
